Name:		rdesktop
Version:	1.5.0
Release:	1
License:	GPL
Group:		X11/Applications/Networking
Source0:	http://dl.sourceforge.net/rdesktop/%{name}-%{version}.tar.gz
# Source0-md5:	433546f60fc0f201e99307ba188369ed
